  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "id": 891,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Multi-leg hedge → Prometheus（本页无 K 线）\n\n| 环节 | 频率 / 说明 |\n|------|-------------|\n| **Prometheus scrape** | **15s**（与 trend 共用 `prometheus.yml` global）|\n| **首行数字** | **`bars/min`** ≈ 每分钟处理几根闭合 bar（5m 平滑）；**`uptime`** = 进程运行秒数（比 `poll次数×30s` 更准确）；**poll 次数**仍为累计 tick。 |\n| **CPU / RSS 曲线** | 紧接首行：**时间序列**可看一段时间内的波动；瞬态 Stat 仍可看当前点。 |\n| **管道** | bars / actions / exec 见各图说明；**无** trend funnel。 |\n\n**strategy / symbol 变量**：`mlbot_multi_leg_bars_processed_total`。"
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · daemon poll tick 次数（累计）",
      "description": "主循环 **`run_forever`** 每轮末尾 **`daemon_polls_total`+1**。**粗算**「轮询节奏」若 `poll_seconds=30` → 约 **`次数×30s` 的 wall 时间**，但 **≠ 精确运行时长**（有 `run_once` 耗时、调度误差）。**请看「进程运行时长」。**",
      "id": 890,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 5, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_multi_leg_daemon_polls_total{job=~\"$job\"}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · 进程运行时长（mlbot_uptime_seconds）",
      "description": "从 **本进程 metrics/uptime 计时起点**算起的秒数；Grafana 可按「秒」读出，再心算分钟/小时，**比 poll×30s 可信**（和部署里 `poll_seconds` 是否改过无关）。",
      "id": 897,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 5, "x": 5, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_uptime_seconds{job=~\"$job\"}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "decimals": 0 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · bars/min（近5m 平均，≈每分钟几根 bar）",
      "description": "**`60 × rate(bars_processed_total[5m])` 之和**。与 **0.017 根/秒**同一信息：÷60 即得；这样直读「每分钟几根」更直观。",
      "id": 893,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 5, "x": 10, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "60 * sum(rate(mlbot_multi_leg_bars_processed_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[5m]))",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none", "decimals": 3 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · CPU %（当前点）",
      "description": "**瞬时值**；看趋势用下面 **CPU 时间序列**。asyncio 休眠多时常贴 0%。",
      "id": 894,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 5, "x": 15, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_cpu_percent{job=~\"$job\"}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · 进程 RSS（MB，当前点）",
      "description": "看趋势用下面 **RSS 时间序列**（与 Stat 同源指标）。",
      "id": 895,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_memory_rss_mb{job=~\"$job\"}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none", "decimals": 0 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · CPU %（历史）",
      "description": "按抓取间隔连续打点；可看尖峰。**与瞬时 Stat 同一 `mlbot_cpu_percent`。**",
      "id": 337,
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_cpu_percent{job=~\"$job\"}", "legendFormat": "CPU %" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent", "min": 0, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 进程 RSS MB（历史）",
      "description": "RSS 取自 exporter；可看内存爬坡/回收。**与瞬时 Stat 同一 `mlbot_memory_rss_mb`。**",
      "id": 338,
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_memory_rss_mb{job=~\"$job\"}", "legendFormat": "RSS MB" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none", "decimals": 0, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 管道：bars（闭合 bar 吞吐）",
      "description": "**仅** `mlbot_multi_leg_bars_processed_total`。**不**单独表示 prefilter 是否通过。",
      "id": 312,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 17 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_bars_processed_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "bars {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 4, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 管道：actions（引擎→编排器意图）",
      "description": "引擎产出的动作（place/cancel/…）进入 orchestrator 的 **批次速率**。**>0 表示在尝试挂单类动作**，不等于一定成交或被风控放行。",
      "id": 332,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 17 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_actions_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "actions {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 4, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 管道：exec + portfolio risk 否决",
      "description": "**exec**：执行管道结果；**risk_rejected**：已通过引擎但被 **组合风控**打的次数。**加仓/开仓**可看下方「事件」面板的 `place` 与本品 **actions/exec** 是否同向抬升（需版本含打点）。",
      "id": 333,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 17 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_execution_results_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "exec {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_risk_rejected_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "risk_rejected {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 4, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 经典漏斗 / orders（多腿不写 trend funnel → 多为 No data）",
      "id": 313,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, stage) (rate(mlbot_funnel_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} · {{stage}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy) (rate(mlbot_orders_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "orders {{strategy}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "C" } } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · ATR / 波动（atr、atr14）",
      "description": "与价格同量级（USDT）的波动代理；**勿**与 0~1 的 chop/box 同轴。",
      "id": 334,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 32 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "mlbot_strategy_feature_value{job=~\"$job\",layer=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\",feature=~\"atr14|atr\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}}/{{symbol}} · {{feature}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none", "decimals": 2, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · Chop / 语义（0~1 及 trend_confidence）",
      "description": "`semantic_chop` / `bpc_semantic_chop` 与 `trend_confidence` 同图（量级相近）。**无** trend 的独立「prefilter 通过/拒绝」计数；`trend_direction` 为离散编码。",
      "id": 335,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 32 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "mlbot_strategy_feature_value{job=~\"$job\",layer=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\",feature=~\"semantic_chop|bpc_semantic_chop|trend_confidence|trend_direction\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}}/{{symbol}} · {{feature}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 3, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · Box prefilter（0/1）",
      "description": "特征里 **box_prefilter** 的数值化展示；**1≈通过盒滤、0≈未通过**（以引擎写入语义为准）。",
      "id": 336,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 32 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "mlbot_strategy_feature_value{job=~\"$job\",layer=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\",feature=\"box_prefilter\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}}/{{symbol}} · box_prefilter"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "max": 1, "decimals": 0, "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "none" } } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · Risk veto by code（governor + symbol_conflict）",
      "id": 319,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 39 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol, code) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_risk_reject_codes_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} {{symbol}} {{code}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 事件（bar_tick / place / risk_reject / symbol_conflict / execution …）",
      "id": 315,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 46 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, event, side) (rate(mlbot_strategy_event_total{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} {{event}} {{side}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 3 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 最近事件价（仅 place/exec 等写入了 price）",
      "id": 316,
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 54 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "mlbot_strategy_event_price{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} {{event}} {{side}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Hedge · 持仓快照",
      "id": 317,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 60 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max by (strategy, symbol, side) (mlbot_position_qty{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"})",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "max by (strategy, symbol, side) (mlbot_position_notional_usdt{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"})",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "showHeader": true }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Hedge · 事件计数（时间轴）",
      "id": 318,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 68 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, event, side) (increase(mlbot_strategy_event_total{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__range]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "showHeader": true }
    }
  ],
